  "feature_bullets_flat": "EASY INSTALLATION: This innovative bath water filter is effortless to install and requires no additional tools or equipment. It can fit seamlessly onto all standard bathtub faucets, making it a convenient addition to any bathroom. Includes two types of handles (standard & flexible) to accommodate any faucet design. CLEAN AND SOFTENED WATER: Activates your cells,Softened water means better hair, skin, and nail condition, while clean water improves circulation and oxygen levels in your blood. Upgrade your shower routine today. EFFICIENT WATER FILTRATION: Enjoy a fast and uninterrupted water filtration with our tub faucet filter,ensuring a smooth refreshing experience every time. WIDE COMPATIBILITY: No matter what type of tub faucet you have, It fits all tubs and cleans water at any temperature for up to 6 months rejuvenating and pure bath experience. PREMIUM CARE: Experience spa-like luxury at home with our bathtub water filter, which provides clean soft water for your body. Say goodbye to odor, dry, itchy skin, dandruff, and eczema, and hello to improved skin, hair, and nail condition.",
